{"tid":1169430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內會通過支持將《逃犯條例》修訂直上大會","createTime":"2019-05-24T11:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T16:11:23.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8cbdc09a3c036cc65e16b12d4ca98afb30d940","tid":1169430,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T11:39:49.000Z","msg":"立法會內務委員會經過約5小時的「特長例會」，在建制派支持之下，以40票贊成，19票反對，通過支持政府繞過法案委員會，將《逃犯條例》修訂直上大會，並通過終止法案委員會的運作。<br />\n<br />\n會議期間，民主派批評建制派配合政府，破壞議會傳統，出賣香港，要求政府盡快撤回草案，先處理台灣殺人案。<br />\n<br />\n建制派就批評民主派將草案妖魔化，千方百計阻撓法案委員會運作，雖然草案直上大會並不理想，但就是唯一出路。<br />\n<br />\n保安事務委員會主席陳克勤表示，會爭取在下周召開特別會議，讓議員可以就修例直接向官員提問。"},{"pid":"c89b0ea72df218ae4fb5af83601e925d77762b9d","tid":1169430,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T11:39:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1106990&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1106990%26csid%3D261_341&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=bcdbc3c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1106990&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"a2d8fb9edcf2a36855f1d6558cd96a6ddf7b2d25","tid":1169430,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T11:41:13.000Z","msg":"今次真係九龍新界冇得避<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f6426902e18bbfee10ed559da0cb8220f475d6","tid":1169430,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T11:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fe7fe52d3d5e07d094d46986d4af600cab8a32","tid":1169430,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T11:51:08.000Z","msg":"點解得19反對 有冇記錄睇吓  要捉鬼"},{"pid":"a40c860784a5d7dd60356bde3706b2c6dc4177f8","tid":1169430,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"